  "title": "Entry-Level B2B Sales (Office Hours, 1-1 Training)",
  "description": "<p><strong>💼 B2B Sales &amp; Marketing Executive</strong><br>\n <em>Entry-Level | 1-on-1 Training | Immediate Start</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking driven and motivated individuals to join our team as <strong>B2B Sales &amp; Marketing Executives</strong>. This is an excellent opportunity for fresh graduates or entry-level candidates looking to build a strong foundation in business sales and client acquisition.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will be part of a dynamic team focused on developing strategic outreach, building long-term client relationships, and delivering effective sales results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engage with business clients to promote services and solutions</li>\n  <li>Identify sales opportunities and convert leads into long-term partnerships</li>\n  <li>Assist in the planning and execution of outreach and marketing strategies</li>\n  <li>Maintain strong client relationships through follow-up and ongoing support</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br>\n✅ Comprehensive training and hands-on mentorship<br>\n✅ Clear career progression and performance-based incentives<br>\n✅ A supportive and professional team environment<br>\n✅ Fixed working hours with work-life balance<br>\n✅ Fresh graduates and ORD personnel are encouraged to apply</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ideal Candidate:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated with a results-driven mindset</li>\n  <li>Eager to learn and grow in a sales-focused role</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Take the first step toward a rewarding career in B2B sales and marketing.</p>\n<p><br>\n<u><strong>📩 Apply today!</strong></u></p>",
